Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.95,0:01:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背上的傷好很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.99,0:01:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了慎重起見\N還是換上新藥好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感激你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.43,0:02:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 要是下次\N又帶這麼重的傷回來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.07,0:02:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不管你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.89,0:02:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六十二話\N京都深刻的記憶\N思緒飛馳的出發點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天要回東京？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是大家一起\N快快樂樂重建的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.70,0:02:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為已經受你們照顧很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.01,0:02:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東京的道場\N差不多該重新開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那無所謂呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.11,0:02:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一個門生的破道場\N有跟沒有都差不多嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.12,0:02:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你講話沒有惡意\N所以我也不與你計較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次你再說我就揍人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天就走太匆忙啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.23,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少等看過中元節的\N大文字火以後再回去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀對呀 就是這個 如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.20,0:03:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是船票已經買了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.97,0:03:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.87,0:03:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.01,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方對劍心而言\N是苦澀的回憶之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.15,0:03:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是\N他以前可是斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.19,0:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那只是過去的事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.26,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在緋村是好人\N沒必要老拖著那個過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也這麼認為 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.37,0:03:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家在那邊死氣沉沉的幹嘛\N應該一起快樂高興才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去\N你們兩人會沉到谷底的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.38,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 兩人講的都很有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.75,0:03:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣吧\N聽我一個老人之言如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定今天花上一天時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.46,0:04:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,參加我\N精心安排的快樂一日游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.99,0:04:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子\N緋村在京都就高興快樂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爺子好主意呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之\N你們想喧嘩起哄就是了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點快點\N叫大家起來 叫大家起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.27,0:04:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心與左之助早就出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出去？兩個人一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有 是分開來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早上我起來就沒看到劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我也要出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.55,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 你要出去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比壑山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.96,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來劍心不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠 你怎麼在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛 不可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來得正好 我有事跟你談\N今天你就陪我一天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.93,0:05:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆 我要買花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 你還沒起床嗎\N我要開門了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 這樣老爺子\N又要心情低落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是志志雄他們以前的基地洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是志志雄的殘黨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.38,0:06:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是來看看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.48,0:06:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧   托你的福我才有午飯吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個好吃 你做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.95,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託小增做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.62,0:06:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 小姐做的\N不知有沒有這麼好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.76,0:06:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.53,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我好像局外人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以至少…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼傻話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.37,0:07:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是打倒一個十本刀的人\N保護大家了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是局外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.54,0:07:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我連志志雄真實\N長什麼樣子都沒見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去劍心與志志雄交手的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.37,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…談話之前\N我要先跟你說謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你替劍心治療傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.54,0:07:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候還是你最可靠\N以後還請多多照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為一句謝謝就沒事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.52,0:07:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是這次\N下次會變成怎樣都不曉得哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.49,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都把劍心當成超人一樣\N相信他絕對沒問題 可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從醫生的觀點來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.83,0:08:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的身體只是運動神經跟\N一般人比起來極為優秀罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.70,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外毫無疑問的\N他跟普通人是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.57,0:08:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論什麼樣的傷\N那傷害都是會累積下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.74,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且劍心不是這一兩天\N才剛開始與人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是勉強過關了 但
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次就算死了也不足為奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.59,0:08:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過十年\N這地方還是一點也沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭 禰彥他沒有事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.65,0:09:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.12,0:09:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.91,0:09:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與那個蝙蝠人交手之後\N我感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我贏了 我很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…被劍心那麼點醒之前\N我卻從未注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.09,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強、與正義\N是不能簡單地畫成等號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.63,0:09:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是不夠成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象小孩一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說 下次就算死了也不足為奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 劍心絕對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.31,0:10:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你  看到劍心拖著\N那種身體回來 你感受如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫生不是什麼都能醫治的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓死人復活\N那是絕不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔了十年的掃墓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像找到供奉的花了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.68,0:11:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所見\N什麼都燒光光 消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 左之助你怎麼知道這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.53,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你是為了確認\N齊藤的生死來這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認為那傢伙會死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.50,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…也不可能活著逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.81,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果是他贏了就跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.15,0:11:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以他那套理論\N是我這個活下來的人勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都不明不白\N結束在那爆災之中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.72,0:11:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.26,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入明治時代\N日本全國都受到潮流擺佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認識我的人多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.40,0:12:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接近這裏\N很容易惹上不必要的爭鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才避開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為這個理由嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.38,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會讓我想起被我殺死\N沉眠在這裏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我總忍不住想避開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一起回東京吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.54,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我終於能下定決心\N來為這墳墓獻上鮮花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你還不早點回東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.21,0:12:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事我不會再說第二遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會再來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.82,0:13:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心其實不是好戰的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.23,0:13:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是就像這次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他往往奮不顧身\N不認清自己的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就衝入漩渦之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後總有一天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.87,0:13:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.01,0:13:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.74,0:13:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給自己心情做總結時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.22,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必需更堅強 平時就\N專心祈禱劍心能活著回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的生死\N本來就是無法左右的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.16,0:13:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是往往求生意志強烈的人\N是那活下來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.47,0:13:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 劍心不是那種\N對人生輕言放棄的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.87,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是個心軟的人\N不會為了大家而拋棄性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.58,0:13:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是把劍心從戰鬥的\N瀕死絕境帶回來的不是別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.28,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你\N劍心在東京唯一說再見的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.72,0:14:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好了 你若是像那時候那樣\N又做出消極的舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我是不會原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想說這些 懂了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必道謝了\N我是為了劍心才說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛 你又哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是愛哭鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然…只好超越了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超越？你是說超越齊藤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.17,0:14:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 不光是力量\N各方面都要超越他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.24,0:15:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 左之助其實不是\N很想確認齊藤的生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是來為他與齊藤未完的決鬥\N做個了結的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後他找出以超越\N來取代求勝的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 超越呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縱然不夠成熟\N也要超越他 向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告別消極的自我  向前進呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.20,0:15:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣做才可能接近劍心他們\N接近更厲害的那群男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都地方真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對吧\N是你說到京都就交給你帶路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個山坡爬五趟了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口 你這小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.87,0:16:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏碰見你們真是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.71,0:16:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥迷路了\N請帶我們去葵屋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個笨蛋\N會迷路就別出門算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.25,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 真罕見耶\N沒想到你會跟狐貍精走一塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰狐貍精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.72,0:16:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家在這裏做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.06,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒做什麼 這個笨蛋迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰笨蛋   迷路的人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你大清早跑去哪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃 我去給老朋友掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 剛才你說呃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.21,0:16:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了 你說呃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒聽到你講呃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.62,0:16:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 劍心的傷還沒好\N別太粗魯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話 好久沒聽到了的感覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.73,0:17:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心果然回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.77,0:17:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁大人 可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.41,0:17:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好不容易規畫好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長期以來謝謝你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.45,0:17:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是一樣不親近人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.83,0:17:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子從過去奔跑到現在\N這次正好休養一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他休息個夠吧\N以後他自然又會想奔跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.91,0:17:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫 我們要在此告別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會的話\N下次再一起喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我過敏 不能喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茶水的話…\N以後有機會一起喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 謝謝你來送行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.60,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請代我對翁爺爺說\N謝謝他買的車票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了一個人以外\N大家都沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫他就麻煩你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.36,0:18:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次來京都\N到時候我們再好好的玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 你也可以來東京玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.07,0:18:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.83,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見 小操 你一定要來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.91,0:18:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.81,0:18:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 謝謝你的種種照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 要好好保重哦\N我們等你來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.36,0:19:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的、真的謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.58,0:19:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不告訴他們你平安\N這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他們很在意你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.92,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我與拔刀齊只是一時的聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務完畢之後就沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.53,0:19:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是彼此都背著\N戰鬥中人的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.07,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會的話   遲早會再碰頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.97,0:19:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果到時是敵人\N那也無話可說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話\N幕末時代沒有了斷的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時就能分出結果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.62,0:20:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後會安靜些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.92,0:20:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是火熱耀眼\N卻又溫柔善良的人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.80,0:20:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生了好多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.68,0:20:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.45,0:20:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.56,0:20:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒走這條路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久前還待在京都\N這是當然的呀 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 不覺得肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.64,0:21:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們寄信給玄齊先生與小妙\N說今天要回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會準備飯菜等我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎 太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好久沒這樣一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心？你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.46,0:21:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我害怕自己體內的拔刀齊\N不想牽累大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.86,0:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定過原本的流浪生活\N而離開這裏的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又好像理所當然的\N與大家一起回來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不禁覺得很不可思議…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你記得這地方嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是那天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心向我說再見的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.22,0:21:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候 我什麼也沒對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.46,0:21:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以這次我要說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了

